er content. User then tabs to get out of the \"Skip to main content\" button and focus then goes to the banner button which skips over the banner heading.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior:**\r\nMove the \"Skip to main content\" button to after the banner content is announced.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"2240\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-02-21 at 12 57 55 PM\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/54281166/155006922-a32faa52-acfd-4de8-ad76-c90d2b60349d.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Component(s) impacted\r\n\r\n`dotcom-shell`\r\n\r\n### Browser\r\n\r\nChrome\r\n\r\n### Carbon for IBM.com version\r\n\r\nv1.16.0\r\n\r\n### Severity\r\n\r\nSeverity 3 = The problem is visible or noticeable to users but does not impede the usability or functionality. Affects minor functionality, has a workaround.\r\n\r\n### Application/website\r\n\r\nhttps://carbon-design-system.github.io/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/canary/web-components/?path=/story/components-dotcom-shell--with-universal-banner\r\n\r\n### Package\r\n\r\n@carbon/ibmdotcom-web-components\r\n\r\n### CodeSandbox example\r\n\r\nNA\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce the issue (if applicable)\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Release date (if applicable)\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Code of Conduct\r\n\r\n- [X] I agree to follow this project's [Code of Conduct](https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/blob/main/.github/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md)\r\n- [X] I checked the [current issues](https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/issues) for duplicate issues","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/issues/8347/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/issues/8347/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null,"score":1},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/issues/6436","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/issues/6436/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/issues/6436/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/issues/6436/events","html_url":"https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/issues/6436","id":926775060,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU5MjY3NzUwNjA=","number":6436,"title":"[Universal banner] design, dev & usage documentation ","user":{"login":"wonilsuhibm","id":30183447,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMwMTgzNDQ3","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/30183447?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/wonilsuhibm","html_url":"https://github.com/wonilsuhibm","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wonilsuhibm/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wonilsuhibm/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wonilsuhibm/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wonilsuhibm/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wonilsuhibm/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wonilsuhibm/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wonilsuhibm/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wonilsuhibm/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wonilsuhibm/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":1417018577,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxNDE3MDE4NTc3","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/labels/Feature%20request","name":"Feature request","color":"a2eeef","default":false,"description":"A new adopter requested feature"},{"id":1536993691,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxNTM2OTkzNjkx","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/labels/design","name":"design","color":"efe00e","default":false,"description":"Applied to all issues assigned to the design team members.  Filter used in planning meetings"},{"id":1536995735,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxNTM2OTk1NzM1","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/labels/priority:%20medium","name":"priority: medium","color":"4a6bc4","default":false,"description":""},{"id":1595276740,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxNTk1Mjc2NzQw","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/labels/epic","name":"epic","color":"3E4B9E","default":false,"description":""},{"id":2223331671,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwyMjIzMzMxNjcx","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/labels/adopter:%20Innovation%20Team","name":"adopter: Innovation Team","color":"239aa0","default":false,"description":"used when component or pattern will be used by this adopter"}],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":5,"created_at":"2020-05-20T19:53:41Z","updated_at":"2021-11-08T15:41:44Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"## Task\n\nA universal is **the only component allowed to show up above Dotcom masthead**, and should be used for exclusively global and critical announcements. \n\nA prototype universal banner has been built for THINK 2021 in Carbon. And previously v18's universal banner has been used for to communicate other global events / announcements such as  COVID and THINK. As a design system, we need to add it to the library as a reusable component, complete with:\n\n1. a cleaned up design\n2. updated implementation\n3. usage documentation on our website\n\n\n### Content \n\nA universal banner could need the following content. Some fields might be optional. \n\n - heading\n - optional subheading\n - media (image, video, loop)\n - CTA text (button or link)\n\n### Examples\n\n**THINK 2021**\nNPM package: \n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15144993/122942124-f57fe000-d343-11eb-9a1a-713ed87f8493.png)\n\n\n**THINK 2020**\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/30183447/82491057-21ca8c80-9ab2-11ea-854f-51f981de5c3b.png)\n\n**COVID-19 Response**\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/30183447/82491216-5b9b9300-9ab2-11ea-900d-b65253ec706d.png)\n\n#### Additional Information\n- [Final design and design specs](https://ibm.ent.box.com/folder/142303458357?s=fas5qv5zrscudr63y85g28v0k657p83u)\n- [Functional specs](https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom-website/wiki/Universal-banner)","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/issues/6436/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon-for-ibm-dotcom/issues/6436/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null,"score":1}]}}